Free/Open source church worship & presentation software

http://kworship.org

=================
 About
=================

KWorship is meant to be fully featured and to integrate well into KDE.
It is not currently fit for purpose.

James Hogan
Original developer

=================
 Main components
=================

KWorship is divided into a number of key components.

-----------------
 kworship
-----------------
Main kworship application, which is split further into:
 * css
 * display
 * media
 * playlist
 * songdb

-----------------
 unipresent
-----------------
Abstraction of control for different presentation software.
This isn't written yet.

Backends include:
 * MS Powerpoint
 * OO.org Impress
 * kpresenter
 * kworship's display

